lead_paragraph: Pierre-Alexandre Parenteau had a goal and an assist and the Toronto Maple Leafs earned their first victory in nearly two weeks, topping the Carolina Hurricanes 3-1 on Thursday night.

headline.main: Parenteau Lifts Maple Leafs Past Hurricanes 3-1
